# [LAKE](../wg/lake.html)

## Summary
The LAKE Interim Meeting (interim-2026-lake-01) focused on progress updates for active Working Group drafts, formal verification analyses of Remote Attestation over EDHOC, lightweight authorization, and post-quantum (PQ) deployment scenarios. Key highlights included the formal verification of `draft-ietf-lake-ra` using Sapic+, expert evaluation of parallel formal verification efforts, progress toward Working Group Last Calls (WGLC), and the presentation of the Post-Quantum ad-hoc Design Team's analysis of constrained device deployment scenarios.

